Hilliard Davidson PTO PTO Can You Help Campaign:  In lieu of asking students and families to participate in fundraisers throughout the year, the PTO runs an annual CAN YOU HELP! campaign.  The PTO gives 25% of donations back to the freshman, sophomore, junior, and senior classes that are used for their Senior Class Gift upon graduation.  Any and all donations are appreciated and always put to good use.  When donating, if you wish to designate your gift to your student’s year, please indicate so on your check or PayPal memo line.
